==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[plumula]]'', diminutive of ''[[pluma]]'' "feather"; compare French ''[[plumule]]''.

===Noun===
'''plumule'''
# {{botany}} The first [[bud]], or [[gemmule]], of a young [[plant]]; the bud, or growing point, of the [[embryo]], above the [[cotyledon]]s.
# {{zoology}} A down [[feather]].
# {{zoology}} The [[aftershaft]] of a feather.
# {{zoology}} One of the featherlike [[scale]]s of certain male [[butterfly|butterflies]].

